===Noun phrase===
'''[[hit]] and [[run]]'''
# the act of [[hitting]] something or someone with a [[vehicle]] and leaving the [[scene]] of the [[incident]]
# the act of [[joining]] a [[poker]] [[game]], quickly [[winning]] several [[hand]]s, then [[leaving]]
#{{baseball}} a play in which the [[baserunner]]s are put in [[motion]] before the ball is hit
